author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
In Adam's most recent visit to Fonco Studios, Fon Davis shows us how his team made use of 3D modeling and 3D printing to quickly prototype and fabricate hand puppets for a TV show pilot!

Learn about Fonco Studio's projects and fabrication services at https://foncostudios.com/
Follow Fonco on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/foncostudios/

Shot by Joey Fameli and edited by Norman Chan
